Only 5 of 18 services have upstream blocks and proxy_pass rules. The
remaining 13 are reachable directly with no rate limiting, no auth
enforcement, and no security headers.

Implementation:
- Add upstream blocks for all 13 missing services:

    upstream auth_service        { server auth-service:3011; }
    upstream billing_service     { server billing-service:3012; }
    upstream developer_portal    { server developer-portal:3013; }
    upstream trading_service     { server trading-service:3014; }
